l.co.uk/Extra/hanzo60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Best Pens For Inking + Markers</span><hr size=1> I'm sure this question has been awswered in the past, but I was wondering what you think or know are the best technical pens you can buy for inking, since it's about time I bought myself some that actually worked well for more than 10 times before running out of ink flow.<br>
<br>
